                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nom<ex>en</ex></expan>, daz si ewch
                                <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> in
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>dechtnuss</expan> gehabt
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>. Und <expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan> zu
                        disen <expan>zeit<ex>en</ex></expan> mit ewch niht zu schiken
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> denn gut.
